song_lyrics: Sant milan ko jāīe, taj mān moh abhimān;
Jyo jyo pāv āge dhare, koṭi yagna samān.
Mil jāoge āp kahī na kahī,
Tumhe ḍhūnḍh hī lege kahī na kahī.. Man° ṭek
Mil jāoge āp kahī na kahī... Man° 1
Mil jāoge āp kahī na kahī... Man° 2
Hame darashan doge kahī na kahī... Man° 3
title: Man Mohan mūrat terī Prabhu
